<% content_for :title, "Cancellations & Refunds — Help" %>

<div class="flex gap-8 lg:gap-12">
  <aside class="hidden lg:block w-52 flex-shrink-0">
    <%= render "sidebar" %>
  </aside>

  <article class="min-w-0 flex-1">
    <%= render BreadcrumbComponent.new(items: [
      { label: "Help", path: help_path },
      { label: "Cancellations & Refunds", path: nil }
    ]) %>

    <h1 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold text-stone-900">Cancellations & Refunds</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-stone-500">How to cancel a booking and what to expect for your refund.</p>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-8 text-stone-700">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900">How to Cancel</h2>
        <div class="mt-3 space-y-3">
          <p>
            Go to <strong>My Bookings</strong> in the top navigation. Find the booking you want to cancel
            and click <strong>Cancel Booking</strong>. Before the cancellation is finalised, you'll see a
            confirmation message explaining whether you're eligible for a refund.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900">Refund Policy</h2>
        <div class="mt-3">
          <p class="mb-4">The refund you receive depends on how far in advance you cancel:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-4 rounded-xl border border-stone-200 bg-white p-5">
            <li>
              <p class="font-semibold text-stone-900">More than 24 hours before your session</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-stone-600">
                Full refund issued automatically to your original payment method.
                Refunds typically appear within 5–10 business days depending on your bank.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li class="border-t border-stone-100 pt-4">
              <p class="font-semibold text-stone-900">24 hours or less before your session</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-stone-600">
                A <strong>$50 cancellation fee</strong> applies. The remaining balance is refunded
                automatically to your original payment method. The app shows you the exact refund
                amount before you confirm, so there are no surprises.
              </p>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900">Studio-Initiated Cancellations</h2>
        <div class="mt-3 space-y-3">
          <p>
            If the studio cancels your booking for any reason — equipment issues, scheduling conflicts,
            emergencies — you will receive a full refund automatically, regardless of the cancellation
            window. You'll also receive a push notification if you have them enabled.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900">What Happens to the Freed Slots</h2>
        <div class="mt-3 space-y-3">
          <p>
            When a booking is cancelled — by you or by the studio — those hours are immediately
            released back to the calendar as open slots. Any customers on the
            <%= link_to "waitlist", help_waitlist_path, class: "underline hover:text-stone-900" %>
            are automatically notified by email so they can book right away.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</div>
